1
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:21,760
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

2
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:27,140
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

3
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:33,670
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

4
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,400
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 7]

7
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:43,980
The client for this mission disappeared.

8
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:47,500
And it's also a mission
I've yet to complete.

9
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:51,140
It's your mission?

10
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:53,660
Yes.

11
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:00,660
Due to the client's disappearance,

12
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:03,260
there's been no closure till now.

13
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:06,260
The reason I've singled
the three names out

14
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:08,100
is to quickly identify the client

15
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,180
and uncover the truth
about what happened back then.

16
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,260
If it weren't for you that day,

17
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:15,860
I would have caught the client.

18
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:22,260
So you were chasing the client?

19
00:01:23,420 --> 00:01:23,980
Yes.

20
00:01:35,540 --> 00:01:37,660
If Xiaosheng did kill my parents,

21
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:40,540
how am I supposed
to deal with the conflict

22
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:42,180
of revenge and the grace
of him raising me?

23
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:44,940
But why did Xiaosheng claim

24
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,660
that it was Mr. Cao who hired him
to kill my family?

25
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:50,860
It seems staying with the Gang
is the only way to find the truth.

26
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:04,020
Mengchen?

27
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,460
Dr. Qi, where are you dragging me to?

28
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:15,300
I've got things to do.

29
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:16,220
You'll see when we get there.

30
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,020
Just right ahead.

31
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:18,820
Where are we going?

32
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:19,700
What ahead?

33
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:20,700
I don't want to have tea with you.

34
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:21,700
Hurry up.

35
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:28,340
Look, do they look alike?

36
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:31,940
Yeah.

37
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:33,780
Does she look like Mengchen?

38
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:36,580
A new opera troupe
is performing at Fengchun Theater.

39
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,060
The troupe's Dan, Qiaomei,

40
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:39,980
surprised me the first time I saw her.

41
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:42,340
She looks so much like Mengchen.

42
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:44,580
One is as pure as a white lotus.

43
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:46,060
The other is as charming as a red peony.

44
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,220
I like both of them. What should I do?

45
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:49,820
Don't mess with Mengchen.

46
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:52,860
So, you're saying

47
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:54,340
Qiaomei is a better match for me?

48
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:55,540
Don't mess with her, either.

49
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,460
Why?

50
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,340
That's a bit too much.

51
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:21,620
[Jinmei Building]

52
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:24,940
Dr. Qi, you're here for tea as well?

53
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,140
Yes.

54
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:29,580
Oh, thanks for the medicine
you gave me earlier.

55
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,780
My throat's been much better.

56
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:34,300
No biggie, Madam.

57
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:35,580
It was my pleasure

58
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:38,580
to help.

59
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:44,380
What are you doing?
Can't you see she's not Mengchen?

60
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:10,180
Master, are you still mad?

61
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,940
You're making a mountain
out of a molehill.

62
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:19,700
That was a Western etiquette

63
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,780
called hand-kissing.

64
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,260
It's a sign of respect.

65
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,140
No wonder.

66
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,260
You know proper etiquette,

67
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,780
unlike those Westerners

68
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:35,220
who are all about hugging and kissing,

69
00:04:35,540 --> 00:04:36,660
and always taking liberties.

70
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,220
Master,

71
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:43,180
I heard they don't just do hand-kissing

72
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,260
but also cheek-kissing.

73
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:47,420
How about...

74
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,860
I will show you,

75
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,580
Master?

76
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:01,780
Starting tomorrow, I'll be training you.

77
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:10,100
I'll only demonstrate this once,
so watch closely.

78
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:33,460
Wait a second.

79
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,220
Your body should be like this.

80
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:07,190
