♪Shielding the tiles from wind and rain♪

189
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:11,520
♪Garments swept over the flowing water,
pristine and clean♪

190
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:17,340
♪Swinging through autumn
to Stone Bridge Bay♪

191
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:23,500
♪In the land of dreams,
love sparks into wildfire♪

192
00:13:24,570 --> 00:13:29,340
♪Radiant as the night sky,
setting the city aflame♪

193
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,550
♪Though trapped in deep mud,♪

194
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:35,600
♪I fear no changes♪

195
